<template>
    <app-hero :heroes="heroes"/>
</template>

<script>
import AppHero from "../components/AppHero";
import axios from "axios";
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      heroes: []
    }
  },
  mounted() {
    axios
        .get('https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/photos')
        .then(response => this.heroes = response.data)
  },
  name: "AppMainBlock",
  components: {AppHero}
}
</script>
